{"tid":1726844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人準備含撚啦","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:35:30.000Z","uid":229289,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f83f62a071b7948c5da39ec450b5e4710873c94","tid":1726844,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"老解今次走出個豬欄 自發清理路障 <br />\n下次就周街行 不再受限 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e45a1ef40014ab726f27af1d126128d43af0e5","tid":1726844,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係美國戰線阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地藍屍撐由佢地，佢係係咪都奶共架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大件事 唔好玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國會美中經濟與安全審議委員會發表年度報告，表示若果中國對香港出動解放軍或武警干預香港局勢，美國國會應該撤銷《美國-香港政策法》給予香港獨立關稅區的特殊地位。"},{"pid":"3d7df70e95428d8cf8a547a6618b8ab13023670c","tid":1726844,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔理做咩任務都好 出咗老解就係出咗老解<br />\n即使只係出嚟執磚或者掃地<br />\n我哋唔可以當佢係普通市民咁對待<br />\n只要發生衝突或者口角 都一定唔係當普通口角衝突處理<br />\n最少佢哋會有特權有班黑警保護<br />\n發生咩事都一定係市民錯 嚴重的話甚至當你搞軍隊<br />\n<br />\n係呢個情況下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原則上係解放軍已經出動</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0525026d6ff0629062f181589689fb8bc752934","tid":1726844,"uid":266741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f83f62a071b7948c5da39ec450b5e4710873c94","tid":1726844,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"老解今次走出個豬欄 自發清理路障 <br />\n下次就周街行 不再受限 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/